item.title: Let's 2019 Begin
item.description: Happy New Year 2019 🎆 Yeah first post of the year. Let me wish you a Happy New Year. Big project, big work, big ambition, this year will be exciting! What super fun thing am I planning to do in 2019 ? Read more books 📚 Train more ElePHPhant in PHP 🐘 Starting to interest in Django Framework 🦎 Maintain XPlaneLover✈️ & MyBearIsYellow 🐻 Blog Find a project to contribute in Open Source regularly That’s the kinda thing, I’m gonna to do…
